Program: Outlook
Title: 30/11/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0053hm8
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 1 Dec 2009
Personal stories behind the news from all over the world. With Matthew Bannister. Wife of the Washington sniper; Indian puppeteers colony Mildred Muhammad The ex wife of John Muhammad - the Washington sniper - tells presenter Matthew Bannister why she believes the shooting spree he was involved in was an elaborate plan to kill her. She tells Matthew Banister why she believes this and about the events leading up to John's execution. Puppeteer Colony Suhail Haleem has been to meet Babubhai Bhaat, a folk musician and one of the earliest settlers of a colony of artists and puppeteers in New Delhi which is under threat from a government slum clearance. Show less